config BR2_PACKAGE_STATUS_MONITOR
    bool "status-monitor"
    help
      PureFox system status monitor daemon.
      
      This package provides a lightweight C daemon that monitors
      system status including audio services, ALSA configuration,
      and volume levels. It writes status to a JSON file for
      efficient web interface polling.
      
      Features:
      - Monitors active audio services (NAA, RAAT, MPD, etc.)
      - Tracks ALSA output configuration (I2S/USB)
      - Reports volume and mute status
      - Minimal CPU usage (C implementation)
      - JSON output for web interface